  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the dose of drug which is most effective in the
      delineation of dead heart muscle.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study has previously been posted by Berlex, Inc. Berlex, Inc. has been renamed to Bayer
      HealthCare Pharmaceuticals, Inc.Bayer HealthCare Pharmaceuticals, Inc.is the sponsor of the
      trial.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
